   TOKYO -- Sumitomo Chemical Co. said it will set up a
subsidiary in Paris in October to strengthen its agricultural
chemical businesses for the European market unification
planned for 1992.
   Officials of the Japanese chemical manufacturer said
Sumitomo Chemical France S.A. will sell finished products in
